[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LADSPA LADSPA] effects can be assigned to either an individual instrument on the  [[0.4:Instrument Editor#The_FX_tab|instrument's FX-tab]] or assigned to an FX-channel in the [[0.4:FX Mixer|FX Mixer]].

Clicking the "'''Add effect'''" button below the Effect Chains box opens following dialog: 

http://lmms.sourceforge.net/wiki/images/2/25/Add-effect.png

Double-click to select an effect. <br> 
You can narrow the list of effects using the text box at the top (e.g. "filter", "delay", etc). <br>

